Summary: Flashing lights, 2 objects in sky, slight movement.
divs: sighting detailslooking at the moon from my window, noticed the lights which have been there before. when i first noticed i immidately thought it was an aeroplane, but it did not move for a few hours. there were flashing lights of red and green and golden which made me think of a plane. there were two objects, one below the other, the bottom one bigger and brighter. the top object\lights remained stationary whilst the bottom moved from left to right occationally. i was fairly scared because i could not identify it as anything normal such as an aeroplane. i watched it for around wenty minutes then went inside out of fear of being alone. i checked every so often for a while but the object remained, still flashing and then i went to bed.
